9. accounting for suspended exploratory well costs
the corporation continues capitalization of exploratory well costs beyond one year after the well is completed if (a)the well found a
sufficient quantity of reserves to justify its completion as a producing well and (b)sufficient progress is being made in assessing the reserves and the economic and operating viability of the project.
